{"tid":2133551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"62歲手足被加控2項罪名","createTime":"2020-07-31T07:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T07:02:38.000Z","uid":231886,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"79522a9a1e006a06247bf992a062901fe0654a20","tid":2133551,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"62歲男子涉向上水警察宿舍擲汽油彈 被加控兩項罪名<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">一名62歲男子涉嫌於3月向上水已婚警察宿舍投擲汽油彈</span>，案件早在粉嶺裁判法院再訊。他除了被控縱火，再被加控管有腐蝕性物品及管有物品意圖作非法用途使用兩項罪名，裁判官將案押後至8月20日，<span class=\"red\">被告沒有申請擔保，須繼續還押</span>。案情指，被告於本年3月23日，在上水已婚警察宿舍外非法以火損壞屬於高級警員的私家車。被<span class=\"red\">告當日於宿舍外的單車徑管有鹽酸及一把鋤頭，因此被加控兩項罪名。</span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，黑警死全家呀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200323/LX4VH5FLPLBWT3J2WVXHPDUXEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200323%2FLX4VH5FLPLBWT3J2WVXHPDUXEA%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG14gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=b8d5a186\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200323%2FLX4VH5FLPLBWT3J2WVXHPDUXEA%2F&h=de1f8dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200323/LX4VH5FLPLBWT3J2WVXHPDUXEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1Kdgbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1Kdgbw.jpg&h=8b5039c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"519f1f81645fdb959a491882bb1a632eb253598b","tid":2133551,"uid":316420,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足年紀好大"},{"pid":"3aa1933b910fc49de27ec7a97cfbf5d78daa87b7","tid":2133551,"uid":231886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"519f1f81645fdb959a491882bb1a632eb253598b","tid":2133551,"uid":316420,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1